msgstr "视频比特率(Mbps)"

#: src/pm-settings-dialog.c:124
msgid "Lower it to save bandwidth. Reconnects to apply."
msgstr "降低它以节省带宽。重新连接后生效。"

#: src/pm-settings-dialog.c:132
msgid "Turn off phone screen"
msgstr "关闭手机屏幕"

#: src/pm-settings-dialog.c:134
msgid ""
"Dark the phone's panel to save battery once you unlock it. Reconnects to "
